<span id="lbl_content">&nbsp;
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span><span>1</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、市场预测</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">普通商品砂浆在具有广阔的市场，以下按四种方法进行市场预测</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按定额砂浆用量推算</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按定额计算多层住宅砂浆用量为</span><span><span>0.198m3/m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">（建筑面积），高层住宅砂浆用量为</span><span><span>0.0889m3/m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，按多层住宅与高层住宅建筑面积</span><span><span>7</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：</span><span><span>3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">来计算，则每平方建筑需使用砂浆</span><span><span>0.16527m3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，按每年</span><span><span>2000</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万</span><span><span>m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的住宅建设规模计算，则需使用砂浆</span><span><span>330.54</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万</span><span><span>m3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，折算成干粉为</span><span><span>578.45</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨，由于定额计算量与实际使用量存在一定的差距，如按增加</span><span><span>30％</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">计算，则需要干粉砂浆</span><span><span>752</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按工程实际使用量推算，以下为一个</span><span><span>100m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">建筑面积住宅单元的普通干粉砂浆的使用量推算</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">砂浆种类、用途、用量</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">外墙砌筑：砌筑</span><span><span>25 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">立方米砖砌体，</span></span><span><span><span>25m3*0.26*1.75<br />
11.4</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">内墙砌筑：砌筑</span><span><span>20 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">立方米砖砌体，</span></span><span><span><span>20m3*0.26*1.75<br />
9.1</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">外墙抹灰：</span><span><span>120 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米抹灰，</span><span><span>30mm</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">厚，</span></span><span><span><span>120m2*0.03m*1.75<br />
6.3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">内墙抹灰：</span><span><span>210 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米抹灰，包括天棚，</span><span><span>20mm</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">厚，</span></span><span><span><span>210m2*0.02m*1.75<br />
7.4</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">地坪砂浆：</span><span><span>70 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米地坪找平，</span><span><span>50mm</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">厚，</span></span><span><span><span>70m2*0.05m*1.75<br />
6.1</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">合计：</span><span><span> <span>40</span></span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按每年</span><span><span>2000</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万</span><span><span>m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的住宅建设规模计算，则需使用干粉砂浆为</span><span><span>800</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨。上述两项推算未包含工业与民用建筑。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按上海地区年水泥用量推算</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">上海地区</span><span><span>2002</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年使用水泥约</span><span><span>1600~1800</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨，按上海水泥散装率约</span><span><span>40％~50％</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">计算，上海地区每年要使用约</span><span><span>800~900</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨包装水泥，如有</span><span><span>400</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨用于建筑砂浆，按水泥与砂</span><span><span>1</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：</span><span><span>2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">计则有近</span><span><span>1200</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨普通干粉砂浆的用量。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按上海地区年商品混凝土用量推算</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">上海地区</span><span><span>2002</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年使用商品混凝土约</span><span><span>2500</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万立方米，按砂浆用量为混凝土用量的</span><span><span>1/4~1/5</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">推算，则需要</span><span><span>500~625</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万立方米的商品砂浆，折合普通干粉砂浆为</span><span><span>875~1100</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">综上所述，按上述四种推算方法预计上海地区全面推广商品砂浆后，每年的使用量在</span><span><span>1000~1200</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨。产值约</span><span><span>17~25</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">亿元。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span><span>2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span><span><span>2003</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年上半年工作情况</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按照本市推广使用商品砂浆的时间节点，上海市建材发展办会同市建委科技委组织专家对推荐上报的第一批预拌（商品）砂浆生产单位进行了新材料认定评审，会同上海市建筑科学研究院对申报企业进行了现场检查。至</span><span><span>2003</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span><span><span>6</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月底，已有九家申报单位获得了《上海市新型建设材料认定证书》，其中预拌砂浆生产单位</span><span><span>7</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">家，年生产能力</span><span><span>80</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万</span><span><span>m3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">（约合</span><span><span>140</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨干粉砂浆），干粉砂浆生产企业</span><span><span>2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">家，年生产能力</span><span><span>40</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨，二者合计已达</span><span><span>180</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万吨。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">上半年，本市同济大学研究生公寓、海运学院学生公寓、华山医院、上海强生</span><span><span>GMP</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">改造工程、新湖明珠城等</span><span><span>16</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">个工程已根据规定使用预拌（商品）砂浆，其中干粉砂浆使用量约</span><span><span>3179</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨，预拌砂浆使用量约</span><span><span>2500m3</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span><span>3. </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">发展趋势</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">改革开放以来，我国的国民经济快速、健康地发展，到目前已实现了第二步的战略目标，达到了小康水平。随着住宅产业化的进程，人们对住宅质量的要求不断提高，人民群众的环保节能意识不断加强，新型墙体材料的广泛使用，这些都必将带动各种特种干粉材料的发展，</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">就目前而言，混凝土界面处理剂、瓷砖粘结剂、内外墙建筑腻子等已被市场所接受而广泛使用。以下为一个</span><span><span>100m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">建筑面积住宅单元的特种干粉材料的使用量推算。</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">砂浆种类、用途、用量</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">界面剂：内外墙</span><span><span>330</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米界面处理，</span></span><span><span><span>330m2*3kg/m2<br />
0.99</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">瓷砖粘结剂：贴瓷砖</span><span><span>70m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，</span></span><span><span><span>70m2*5 kg/m2<br />
0.35</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">外墙腻子：</span><span><span>120 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米，</span><span><span>2mm</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">厚，</span></span><span><span><span>120m2*2.5 kg/m2<br />
0.30</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">内墙腻子：</span><span><span>210 </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平方米（包括天棚），</span><span><span>2mm</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">厚，</span></span><span><span><span>210m2*2.5 kg/m2<br />
0.53</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">合计：</span><span><span>2.17</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨</span><span></span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;background:white;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">
	<span><span style="font-family:宋体;">按每年</span><span><span>2000</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万</span><span><span>m2</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的住宅建设规模计算，则需使用上述特种干粉为</span><span><span>40</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">多万吨。以上还未包括二次装修以及其他工业与民用建筑所需的特种干粉材料。</span></span><span></span> 
</p>
</span>